{
  "annotations": { "list": [{ "builtIn": 1, "datasource": { "type": "grafana", "uid": "-- Grafana --" }, "enable": true, "hide": true, "iconColor": "rgba(0, 211, 255, 1)", "name": "Annotations & Alerts", "type": "dashboard" }] },
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 0,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "liveNow": false,
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "About this dashboard",
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 16, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "options": { "mode": "markdown", "content": "NAT Gateway networking health and **estimated** data-processing cost for a single Data Platform account, from auto-published CloudWatch metrics (no setup needed). Pick an **Account** at the top.\n\nCloudWatch usage metrics are used to **estimate** NAT Gateway data-processing costs at the current eu-west-2 rate of **$0.05/GB**. These figures are estimates only and do **not** include:\n\n- NAT Gateway hourly charges ($0.05 per NAT Gateway-hour)\n- Internet data-transfer charges\n- Cross-Availability Zone data-transfer charges\n- Other AWS networking charges\n\n**AWS Cost Explorer and the Cost & Usage Report (CUR) remain the source of truth for billing.** Watch for NAT **port-allocation errors** (SNAT exhaustion) and **packets dropped** in the rows below." }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Cost caveats",
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 0 },
      "options": { "mode": "markdown", "content": "- Costs shown are **estimates only**.\n- Based on CloudWatch usage metrics.\n- **Data processing only** (excludes hourly, data-transfer and cross-AZ charges).\n- Actual billing comes from **AWS Cost Explorer / CUR**." }
    },
    { "id": 3, "type": "row", "title": "At a glance", "collapsed": false, "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 6 }, "panels": [] },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Active connections",
      "description": "Peak concurrent active connections across all NAT gateways in the window (ActiveConnectionCount). Each gateway supports up to ~55,000 simultaneous connections per unique destination, so a high or climbing count is the leading indicator of NAT saturation and impending SNAT port-allocation errors.",
      "datasource": { "type": "cloudwatch", "uid": "${account}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 0, "y": 7 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "color": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "blue" } }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area", "justifyMode": "auto", "orientation": "auto", "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["max"], "fields": "", "values": false }, "textMode": "auto" },
      "targets": [
        { "datasource": { "type": "cloudwatch", "uid": "${account}" }, "refId": "A", "region": "eu-west-2", "namespace": "AWS/NATGateway", "queryMode": "Metrics", "metricQueryType": 1, "metricEditorMode": 1, "sqlExpression": "SELECT SUM(ActiveConnectionCount) FROM \"AWS/NATGateway\"" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Peak bytes out",
      "description": "Highest per-period total of bytes sent to destinations (egress to the internet) across all NAT gateways in the window (BytesOutToDestination).",
      "datasource": { "type": "cloudwatch", "uid": "${account}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 4, "y": 7 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "bytes", "color": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "blue" } }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area", "justifyMode": "auto", "orientation": "auto", "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["max"], "fields": "", "values": false }, "textMode": "auto" },
      "targets": [
        { "datasource": { "type": "cloudwatch", "uid": "${account}" }, "refId": "A", "region": "eu-west-2", "namespace": "AWS/NATGateway", "queryMode": "Metrics", "metricQueryType": 1, "metricEditorMode": 1, "sqlExpression": "SELECT SUM(BytesOutToDestination) FROM \"AWS/NATGateway\"" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Data processed",
      "description": "Total data processed by NAT gateways over the selected window (BytesInFromSource + BytesInFromDestination) — the volume the $0.05/GB data-processing charge is based on.",
      "datasource": { "type": "datasource", "uid": "-- Mixed --" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 8, "y": 7 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "bytes", "color": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "blue" } }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area", "justifyMode": "auto", "orientation": "auto", "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["sum"], "fields": "", "values": false }, "textMode": "auto" },
      "targets": [
        { "datasource": { "type": "cloudwatch", "uid": "${account}" }, "refId": "A", "region": "eu-west-2", "namespace": "AWS/NATGateway", "queryMode": "Metrics", "metricQueryType": 1, "metricEditorMode": 1, "sqlExpression": "SELECT SUM(BytesInFromSource) FROM \"AWS/NATGateway\"", "hide": true },
        { "datasource": { "type": "cloudwatch", "uid": "${account}" }, "refId": "B", "region": "eu-west-2", "namespace": "AWS/NATGateway", "queryMode": "Metrics", "metricQueryType": 1, "metricEditorMode": 1, "sqlExpression": "SELECT SUM(BytesInFromDestination) FROM \"AWS/NATGateway\"", "hide": true },
        { "datasource": { "type": "__expr__", "uid": "__expr__" }, "refId": "C", "type": "math", "expression": "$A + $B" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Estimated data processing cost",
      "description": "Estimated NAT data-processing charge over the selected window: (BytesInFromSource + BytesInFromDestination) converted to GB and multiplied by the eu-west-2 data-processing rate of $0.05/GB. Excludes the $0.05 per NAT Gateway-hour charge and all data-transfer charges. Estimate only — AWS Cost Explorer / CUR is the source of truth.",
      "datasource": { "type": "datasource", "uid": "-- Mixed --" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 12, "y": 7 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "currencyUSD", "decimals": 2, "color": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "green" } }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area", "justifyMode": "auto", "orientation": "auto", "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["sum"], "fields": "", "values": false }, "textMode": "auto" },
      "targets": [
        { "datasource": { "type": "cloudwatch", "uid": "${account}" }, "refId": "A", "region": "eu-west-2", "namespace": "AWS/NATGateway", "queryMode": "Metrics", "metricQueryType": 1, "metricEditorMode": 1, "sqlExpression": "SELECT SUM(BytesInFromSource) FROM \"AWS/NATGateway\"", "hide": true },
        { "datasource": { "type": "cloudwatch", "uid": "${account}" }, "refId": "B", "region": "eu-west-2", "namespace": "AWS/NATGateway", "queryMode": "Metrics", "metricQueryType": 1, "metricEditorMode": 1, "sqlExpression": "SELECT SUM(BytesInFromDestination) FROM \"AWS/NATGateway\"", "hide": true },
        { "datasource": { "type": "__expr__", "uid": "__expr__" }, "refId": "C", "type": "math", "expression": "($A + $B) / 1000000000 * 0.05" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Port-allocation errors",
      "description": "ErrorPortAllocation > 0 means a NAT gateway could not allocate a source port for SNAT — i.e. SNAT port exhaustion from too many simultaneous connections to the same destination. Sustained errors mean connections are failing; spread load across destinations or add NAT gateways.",
      "datasource": { "type": "cloudwatch", "uid": "${account}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 16, "y": 7 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "color": { "mode": "thresholds" }, "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [{ "color": "green", "value": null }, { "color": "red", "value": 1 }] } }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area", "justifyMode": "auto", "orientation": "auto", "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["sum"], "fields": "", "values": false }, "textMode": "auto" },
      "targets": [
        { "datasource": { "type": "cloudwatch", "uid": "${account}" }, "refId": "A", "region": "eu-west-2", "namespace": "AWS/NATGateway", "queryMode": "Metrics", "metricQueryType": 1, "metricEditorMode": 1, "sqlExpression": "SELECT SUM(ErrorPortAllocation) FROM \"AWS/NATGateway\"" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Packets dropped",
      "description": "PacketsDropCount should normally stay at zero. Non-zero values are unusual and may indicate an AWS-side issue or a gateway under stress; investigate if it is persistently above zero.",
      "datasource": { "type": "cloudwatch", "uid": "${account}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 20, "y": 7 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "color": { "mode": "thresholds" }, "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [{ "color": "green", "value": null }, { "color": "orange", "value": 1 }] } }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area", "justifyMode": "auto", "orientation": "auto", "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["sum"], "fields": "", "values": false }, "textMode": "auto" },
      "targets": [
        { "datasource": { "type": "cloudwatch", "uid": "${account}" }, "refId": "A", "region": "eu-west-2", "namespace": "AWS/NATGateway", "queryMode": "Metrics", "metricQueryType": 1, "metricEditorMode": 1, "sqlExpression": "SELECT SUM(PacketsDropCount) FROM \"AWS/NATGateway\"" }
      ]
    },
    { "id": 10, "type": "row", "title": "Traffic", "collapsed": false, "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 11 }, "panels": [] },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "NAT bytes out to destination",
      "description": "Bytes sent from NAT gateways to destinations (egress to the internet) per gateway (BytesOutToDestination).",
      "datasource": { "type": "cloudwatch", "uid": "${account}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 12 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 10, "showPoints": "never" }, "min": 0, "unit": "bytes" }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" } },
      "targets": [
        { "datasource": { "type": "cloudwatch", "uid": "${account}" }, "refId": "A", "region": "eu-west-2", "namespace": "AWS/NATGateway", "queryMode": "Metrics", "metricQueryType": 1, "metricEditorMode": 1, "sqlExpression": "SELECT SUM(BytesOutToDestination) FROM SCHEMA(\"AWS/NATGateway\", NatGatewayId) GROUP BY NatGatewayId ORDER BY SUM() DESC" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "NAT bytes out to source",
      "description": "Bytes sent from NAT gateways back to clients in the VPC (response traffic) per gateway (BytesOutToSource).",
      "datasource": { "type": "cloudwatch", "uid": "${account}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 12 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 10, "showPoints": "never" }, "min": 0, "unit": "bytes" }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" } },
      "targets": [
        { "datasource": { "type": "cloudwatch", "uid": "${account}" }, "refId": "A", "region": "eu-west-2", "namespace": "AWS/NATGateway", "queryMode": "Metrics", "metricQueryType": 1, "metricEditorMode": 1, "sqlExpression": "SELECT SUM(BytesOutToSource) FROM SCHEMA(\"AWS/NATGateway\", NatGatewayId) GROUP BY NatGatewayId ORDER BY SUM() DESC" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "NAT bytes in from source",
      "description": "Bytes received by NAT gateways from clients in the VPC (outbound request traffic) per gateway (BytesInFromSource). Counts towards the data-processing charge.",
      "datasource": { "type": "cloudwatch", "uid": "${account}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 20 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 10, "showPoints": "never" }, "min": 0, "unit": "bytes" }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" } },
      "targets": [
        { "datasource": { "type": "cloudwatch", "uid": "${account}" }, "refId": "A", "region": "eu-west-2", "namespace": "AWS/NATGateway", "queryMode": "Metrics", "metricQueryType": 1, "metricEditorMode": 1, "sqlExpression": "SELECT SUM(BytesInFromSource) FROM SCHEMA(\"AWS/NATGateway\", NatGatewayId) GROUP BY NatGatewayId ORDER BY SUM() DESC" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "NAT bytes in from destination",
      "description": "Bytes received by NAT gateways from destinations (inbound response traffic from the internet) per gateway (BytesInFromDestination). Counts towards the data-processing charge.",
      "datasource": { "type": "cloudwatch", "uid": "${account}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 20 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 10, "showPoints": "never" }, "min": 0, "unit": "bytes" }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" } },
      "targets": [
        { "datasource": { "type": "cloudwatch", "uid": "${account}" }, "refId": "A", "region": "eu-west-2", "namespace": "AWS/NATGateway", "queryMode": "Metrics", "metricQueryType": 1, "metricEditorMode": 1, "sqlExpression": "SELECT SUM(BytesInFromDestination) FROM SCHEMA(\"AWS/NATGateway\", NatGatewayId) GROUP BY NatGatewayId ORDER BY SUM() DESC" }
      ]
    },
    { "id": 15, "type": "row", "title": "Connections", "collapsed": false, "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 28 }, "panels": [] },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "NAT active connections",
      "description": "Average concurrent active connections per NAT gateway (ActiveConnectionCount). Each gateway supports up to ~55,000 simultaneous connections per unique destination, so rising counts are the leading indicator of NAT saturation before SNAT port-allocation errors appear.",
      "datasource": { "type": "cloudwatch", "uid": "${account}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 29 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 10, "showPoints": "never" }, "min": 0, "unit": "short" }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" } },
      "targets": [
        { "datasource": { "type": "cloudwatch", "uid": "${account}" }, "refId": "A", "region": "eu-west-2", "namespace": "AWS/NATGateway", "queryMode": "Metrics", "metricQueryType": 1, "metricEditorMode": 1, "sqlExpression": "SELECT AVG(ActiveConnectionCount) FROM SCHEMA(\"AWS/NATGateway\", NatGatewayId) GROUP BY NatGatewayId ORDER BY AVG() DESC" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "NAT connection attempts",
      "description": "New connection attempts made through each NAT gateway (ConnectionAttemptCount). Compare against established connections to spot failing or rejected connections.",
      "datasource": { "type": "cloudwatch", "uid": "${account}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 8, "y": 29 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 10, "showPoints": "never" }, "min": 0, "unit": "short" }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" } },
      "targets": [
        { "datasource": { "type": "cloudwatch", "uid": "${account}" }, "refId": "A", "region": "eu-west-2", "namespace": "AWS/NATGateway", "queryMode": "Metrics", "metricQueryType": 1, "metricEditorMode": 1, "sqlExpression": "SELECT SUM(ConnectionAttemptCount) FROM SCHEMA(\"AWS/NATGateway\", NatGatewayId) GROUP BY NatGatewayId ORDER BY SUM() DESC" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "NAT established connections",
      "description": "Connections successfully established through each NAT gateway (ConnectionEstablishedCount). A widening gap below connection attempts indicates connections that are failing to establish.",
      "datasource": { "type": "cloudwatch", "uid": "${account}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 29 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 10, "showPoints": "never" }, "min": 0, "unit": "short" }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" } },
      "targets": [
        { "datasource": { "type": "cloudwatch", "uid": "${account}" }, "refId": "A", "region": "eu-west-2", "namespace": "AWS/NATGateway", "queryMode": "Metrics", "metricQueryType": 1, "metricEditorMode": 1, "sqlExpression": "SELECT SUM(ConnectionEstablishedCount) FROM SCHEMA(\"AWS/NATGateway\", NatGatewayId) GROUP BY NatGatewayId ORDER BY SUM() DESC" }
      ]
    },
    { "id": 19, "type": "row", "title": "Errors & saturation", "collapsed": false, "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 37 }, "panels": [] },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "NAT port-allocation errors (SNAT exhaustion)",
      "description": "ErrorPortAllocation per NAT gateway. Any value above zero is SNAT port exhaustion — the gateway ran out of source ports for a destination — and means connections are being dropped. Spread load across destinations or add NAT gateways.",
      "datasource": { "type": "cloudwatch", "uid": "${account}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 38 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 10, "showPoints": "never" }, "min": 0, "unit": "short", "color": { "mode": "thresholds" }, "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [{ "color": "green", "value": null }, { "color": "red", "value": 1 }] } }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" } },
      "targets": [
        { "datasource": { "type": "cloudwatch", "uid": "${account}" }, "refId": "A", "region": "eu-west-2", "namespace": "AWS/NATGateway", "queryMode": "Metrics", "metricQueryType": 1, "metricEditorMode": 1, "sqlExpression": "SELECT SUM(ErrorPortAllocation) FROM SCHEMA(\"AWS/NATGateway\", NatGatewayId) GROUP BY NatGatewayId ORDER BY SUM() DESC" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "NAT packets dropped",
      "description": "PacketsDropCount per NAT gateway. This should normally remain zero; persistent non-zero values are unusual and may indicate an AWS-side issue or a gateway under stress.",
      "datasource": { "type": "cloudwatch", "uid": "${account}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 38 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 10, "showPoints": "never" }, "min": 0, "unit": "short", "color": { "mode": "thresholds" }, "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [{ "color": "green", "value": null }, { "color": "orange", "value": 1 }] } }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" } },
      "targets": [
        { "datasource": { "type": "cloudwatch", "uid": "${account}" }, "refId": "A", "region": "eu-west-2", "namespace": "AWS/NATGateway", "queryMode": "Metrics", "metricQueryType": 1, "metricEditorMode": 1, "sqlExpression": "SELECT SUM(PacketsDropCount) FROM SCHEMA(\"AWS/NATGateway\", NatGatewayId) GROUP BY NatGatewayId ORDER BY SUM() DESC" }
      ]
    }
  ],
